title: Apple Airpod 1st Generation
description: Driven by the custom Apple W1 chip, AirPods use optical sensors and a motion accelerometer to detect when they’re in your ears. Whether you’re using both AirPods or just one, the W1 chip automatically routes the audio and engages the microphone. And when you’re on a call or talking to Siri, an additional accelerometer works with beamforming microphones to filter out background noise and focus on the sound of your voice. Because the ultralow-power W1 chip manages battery life so well, AirPods deliver an incredible 5 hours of listening time on one charge.2 And they’re made to keep up with you, thanks to a charging case that holds multiple additional charges for more than 24 hours of listening time.3 Need a quick charge? Just 15 minutes in the case gives you 3 hours of listening time.4

title: Apple Airpod 2nd Generation
description: Powered by the Apple H1 headphone chip, AirPods use optical sensors and motion accelerometers to detect when they’re in your ears. Whether you’re using both AirPods or just one, the H1 chip automatically routes the audio and engages the microphone. And when you’re on a call or talking to Siri, an additional speech-detecting accelerometer works with beamforming microphones to filter out external noise and focus on the sound of your voice.

title: Apple Airpod 3rd Generation
description: AirPods are lightweight and offer a contoured design. They sit at just the right angle for comfort and to better direct audio to your ear. The stem is 33 per cent shorter than AirPods (2nd generation) and includes a force sensor to easily control music and calls.

title: JBL Tune510BT
description: Feel the rhythm of the beat with JBL Tune510BT wireless headphones featuring crisp, powerful JBL Pure Bass Sound which can be found in the most famous venues all around the world. Easy to use, these headphones provide up to 40 hours of pure pleasure and an extra 2 hours of battery with just 5 minutes of power with the USB-C charging cable. Wirelessly stream high-quality sound from your phone without a messy cord, while multi-point connections allow you to switch effortlessly from one Bluetooth device to another. A lightweight, foldable design allows you to easily carry your headphones on-the-go, combined with soft, padded ear cushions to keep ears comfy all day long. Items delivered: 1 x JBL Tune510BT wireless over-ear headphones in black, type-C USB charging cable, warranty/warning, quick start guide

title: JBL Wave 200 True Wireless Earbuds Black
description: Feel and hear the bass with JBL Deep Bass Sound and listen for up to 20 hours when combined with the charging case, for a more enjoyable everyday routine. The Wave 200TWS have a comfortable, ergonomic design thanks to their in-ear stick form, and with 3 ear tips in different sizes you can ensure an exact fit for your ears for extra comfort and clarity. Get active. Designed to go with your flow featuring 1PX2 water-resistant materials that can stand up to rain and sweat so you can listen at home or while enjoying a high-intensity workout. Dual Connect technology lets you take calls or listen to music with either bud or both; choose which one to use and leave the other one in the case to save battery. Items delivered: 1 x JBL Wave 200TWS in-ear headphones with charging case and JBL Deep Bass Sound, 1 x USB type-C charging cable, 3 x ear tips, 1 x Quick Start Guide and safety sheet, in black
